satyam shivam is a 1981 telugu action film produced by d. venkateswara rao on &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; creations banner and directed by k. raghavendra rao . the film stars n. t. rama rao , akkineni nageswara rao , sridevi , rati agnihotri in the lead roles and music composed by chakravarthy . the film is remake of hindi movie suhaag ( 1979 ) .